Reference Answer: True

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many vases are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many vases are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the vase have an open top?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the vase have an open top?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the vase have a short base?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the vase have a short base?')
ANSWER6=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the vase have a tear-drop shape?')
ANSWER7=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the vase have a tear-drop shape?')
ANSWER8=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Does the vase have handles?')
ANSWER9=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Does the vase have handles?')
ANSWER10=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4} and {ANSWER6} and not {ANSWER8}')
ANSWER11=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5} and {ANSWER7} and not {ANSWER9}')
ANSWER12=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER10} and {ANSWER11}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER12)
```
